Tianjin%20sentenced%20a%20former%20executive%20for%20a%20state-owned%20firm%20to%20death%20for%20bribery%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBai%20Tianhui%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20accepting%20bribes%20worth%20%24151%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20authorities%20said%20he%20helped%20solve%20several%20other%20crimes%20but%20wouldn't%20get%20a%20lighter%20sentence%20for%20that.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20senior%20banker%20for%20a%20Chinese%20state-owned%20asset%20management%20firm%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20death%20for%20bribery%2C%20a%20court%20in%20Tianjin%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBai%20Tianhui%2C%20an%20ex-general%20manager%20of%20China%20Huarong%20International%20Holdings%2C%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20taking%20bribes%20worth%20%24151%20million%20from%202014%20to%202018%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftj2zy.tjcourt.gov.cn%2Farticle%2Fdetail%2F2024%2F05%2Fid%2F7962142.shtml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecourt%20wrote%20in%20an%20announcement.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20said%20Bai%20had%20abused%20his%20position%20as%20a%20holder%20of%20various%20appointments%20at%20his%20firm%20and%20accepted%20bribes%20involved%20with%20project%20acquisitions%20and%20corporate%20financing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20Bai%20took%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20huge%26quot%3B%20bribes%20and%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bcircumstances%20of%20the%20crime%20were%20extremely%20serious%2C%20and%20the%20social%20impact%20was%20extremely%20bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20disgraced%20former%20manager%20cooperated%20with%20authorities%20to%20help%20expose%20and%20solve%20other%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20crimes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Bai%20providing%20what%20the%20court%20said%20were%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20contributions%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20the%20magnitude%20of%20his%20crimes%20was%20so%20great%20he%20would%20not%20receive%20a%20lighter%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExecution%20for%20corruption%20in%20China%20is%20generally%20rare%2C%20and%20those%20who%20have%20received%20such%20a%20sentence%20are%20usually%20deemed%20to%20have%20cost%20the%20country%20considerable%20resources%20through%20their%20crimes.%20Bai%20is%20the%20second%20former%20Huarong%20executive%20to%20be%20handed%20the%20death%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-death-sentence-banker-lai-xiaomin-bribery-bigamy-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELai%20Xiaomin%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20was%20chairman%20of%20the%20firm%2C%20was%20executed%20in%202021%20after%20being%20found%20guilty%20of%20graft%20involving%20about%20%24277%20million.%20He%20was%20also%20charged%20with%20bigamy%20and%20fathering%20two%20illegitimate%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Tianjin%20court%20sentenced%20Lai%20to%20death%20on%20January%205%20of%20that%20year%2C%20and%20he%20was%20executed%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month%20after%20his%20appeal%20was%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20media%20didn't%20say%20if%20Bai%20intends%20to%20appeal%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20rare%20for%20death%20sentences%20in%20China%20to%20be%20overturned.%20One%20former%20vice-mayor%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinadaily.com.cn%2Fa%2F202110%2F29%2FWS617bdf8fa310cdd39bc7232c.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZhang%20Zhongsheng%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20given%20life%20imprisonment%20after%20appealing%20his%20death%20sentence%20for%20bribes%20involving%20%24160%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20Bai's%20personal%20property%20will%20be%20confiscated%2C%20the%20Tianjian%20court%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBai%20and%20several%20of%20his%20top%20colleagues%2C%20including%20Lai%2C%20were%20put%20under%20investigation%20by%20China's%20graft%20watchdog%2C%20the%20Central%20Commission%20for%20Discipline%20Inspection%2C%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20other%20Huarong%20executives%20are%20still%20scheduled%20for%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBai's%20executi