20its%20previous%20high%20of%2049.9%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extreme%20heat%20poses%20a%20significant%20challenge%20for%20many%20Delhi%20residents.%20Authorities%20are%20warning%20of%20water%20shortages%2C%20while%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20highlighted%20the%20severe%20dangers%20to%20health%20of%20such%20extreme%20heat.%20While%20the%20scorching%20temperatures%20are%20concerning%2C%20staying%20indoors%20for%20extended%20periods%20is%20not%20a%20viable%20option%20for%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20population%20who%20rely%20on%20daily%20outdoor%20work%20to%20earn%20a%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20difficulty%20of%20avoiding%20the%20heat%2C%20awareness%20of%20the%20dangers%20and%20their%20symptoms%20is%20crucial.%20Understanding%20the%20negative%20health%20impacts%20of%20this%20weather%20can%20help%20residents%20take%20necessary%20precautions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeat%20is%20a%20silent%20killer%2C%20causing%20numerous%20deaths%20during%20the%20summer.%20How%20does%20the%20body%20respond%20to%20rising%20temperatures%3F%20Let's%20explore%20this%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Your%20Body%20Reacts%20to%20Extreme%20Heat%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20bodies%20have%20two%20main%20mechanisms%20to%20stay%20cool%3A%20vasodilation%20and%20sweating.%20Vasodilation%20widens%20blood%20vessels%20near%20the%20skin's%20surface%2C%20allowing%20heat%20to%20escape.%20Sweating%20cools%20the%20body%20as%20it%20evaporates%2C%20but%20it%20also%20removes%20salts%20vital%20for%20muscle%20function.%20Dehydration%20and%20electrolyte%20imbalance%20can%20lead%20to%20heat%20cramps%2C%20the%20mildest%20heat-related%20illness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%20Cramps%20-%20The%20Warning%20Sign%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeat%20cramps%20are%20characterized%20by%20muscle%20cramps%2C%20typically%20in%20the%20legs%20and%20abdomen.%20This%20occurs%20because%20the%20body%20is%20losing%20fluids%20and%20electrolytes%20faster%20than%20it%20can%20replace%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeat%20Exhaustion%20-%20When%20the%20Body%20Struggles%20to%20Cool%20Down%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20core%20temperature%20rises%20further%2C%20heat%20exhaustion%20sets%20in.%20Symptoms%20include%20heavy%20sweating%2C%20dizziness%2C%20fatigue%2C%20nausea%2C%20headache%2C%20and%20a%20weak%2C%20rapid%20pulse.%20This%20happens%20because%20the%20body%20is%20pumping%20more%20blood%20to%20the%20skin's%20surface%20to%20cool%20down%2C%20leading%20to%20increased%20heart%20rate%20and%20potential%20dehydration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeatstroke%20-%20The%20Most%20Serious%20Threat%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeatstroke%20is%20the%20most%20severe%20heat-related%20illness%20and%20can%20be%20fatal%20if%20left%20untreated.%20If%20core%20temperature%20rises%20above%2040%C2%B0C%20(104%C2%B0F)%2C%20the%20body's%20cooling%20mechanisms%20fail.%20Sweating%20may%20stop%2C%20and%20the%20skin%20may%20become%20hot%20and%20dry.%20Other%20symptoms%20include%20rapid%2C%20shallow%20breathing%2C%20confusion%2C%20slurred%20speech%2C%20and%20seizures.%20In%20severe%20cases%2C%20coma%20or%20death%20can%20occur.%20The%20kidneys%20are%20often%20the%20first%20organs%20to%20fail%2C%20as%20they%20can%20no%20longer%20remove%20toxins%20from%20the%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStaying%20Safe%20During%20a%20Heatwave%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20extreme%20heat%2C%20it's%20crucial%20to%20stay%20hydrated%20by%20drinking%20plenty%20of%20water%20or%20electrolyte-rich%20beverages.%20Avoid%20strenuous%20activity%2C%20wear%20loose-fitting%20clothing%2C%20and%20seek%20air-conditioned%20spaces%20whenever%20possible.%20Be%20aware%20of%20the%20early%20signs%20of%20heat%20illness%20and%20take%20immediate%20action%20if%20you%20experience%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20rising%20global%20temperatures%2C%20extreme%20heatwaves%20are%20becoming%20more%20frequent%20and%20severe.%20Understanding%20how%20your%20body%20reacts%20to%20heat%20and%20taking%20precautions%20can%20help%20you%20stay%20safe%20during%20these%20scorching%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717043040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F059pkdkg_warmer-summer-heatwave-temperature-rise-global-warming-istock_625x300_30_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-50-degree-celsius-feels-like-the-impact-of-scorching-heat-on-health-5776166%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20human%20body%20combats%20extreme%20heat%20through%20vasodilation%20and%20sweating%2C%20but%20these%20mechanisms%20can%20lead%20to%20dehydration%20and%20electrolyte%20imbalances%2C%20causing%20heat%20cramps%2C%20heat%20exhaustion%2C%20and%20potentially%20fatal%20heatstroke.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-50-degree-celsius-feels-like-the-impact-of-scorching-heat-on-health-5776166%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-50-degree-celsius-feels-like-the-impact-of-scorching-heat-on-health-5776166%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-50-degree-celsius-feels-like-the-impact-of-scorching-heat-on-health-5776166%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20claims%20control%20of%20Gaza's%20entire%20land%20border%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717042923000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F7f5c%2Flive%2Fbc8eb920-1e03-11ef-b96a-1bcfc06460e3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1994g22ve9o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Egyptian%20source%20denies%20that%20tunnels%20used%20by%20Hamas%20still%20exist%20on%20the%20country's%20border%20with%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22