C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rijiju%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mungeshpur%20weather%20station%20recorded%20a%20maximum%20temperature%20of%2052.9%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20a%203-degree%20jump%20from%20Tuesday.%20IMD%20Director%20General%20M%20Mohapatra%20told%20NDTV%20that%20officials%20will%20visit%20the%20station%20and%20conduct%20an%20investigation%20of%20the%20readings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extreme%20heat%20in%20Mungeshpur%20could%20also%20have%20been%20caused%20as%20it%20lies%20on%20the%20city's%20outskirts%20and%20is%20among%20the%20first%20areas%20to%20be%20hit%20by%20hot%20winds%20from%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20remains%20sweltering%20in%20a%20heatwave.%20The%20IMD%20this%20week%20issued%20a%20red%20alert%20health%20notice%20for%20the%20capital%2C%20which%20has%20an%20estimated%20population%20of%20more%20than%2030%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alert%20warns%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20high%20likelihood%20of%20developing%20heat%20illness%20and%20heat%20stroke%20in%20all%20ages%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20care%20needed%20for%20vulnerable%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717041360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fbm0ic8ts_delhi-heat-afp_625x300_30_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-heat-error-or-local-factors-investigation-on-after-delhi-records-52-9-degrees-5776220%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20residents%2C%20who%20have%20been%20battling%20a%20severe%20heatwave%20for%20the%20last%202%20weeks%2C%20received%20a%20major%20shock%20when%20the%20weather%20department's%20reading%20reported%20temperatures%20as%20high%20as%2052.9%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20national%20capital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-heat-error-or-local-factors-investigation-on-after-delh