20a%20media%20report%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20overall%20requirement%20of%20suspending%20meal%20service%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccabin%20crew%20members%20must%20buckle%20up%20when%20the%20seat-belt%20sign%20is%20turned%20on%E2%80%9D%2C%20has%20had%20a%20ripple%20effect%20on%20passengers%20and%20crew%2C%20The%20Straits%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESIA%20put%20more%20comprehensive%20safety%20measures%20in%20place%20shortly%20after%20Flight%20SQ321%20from%20London%20to%20Singapore%20experienced%20severe%20turbulence%20on%20May%2021%2C%20leaving%20a%20passenger%20dead%20and%20dozens%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20only%20hot%20drinks%20and%20soup%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20be%20served%20when%20the%20seatbelt%20sign%20was%20turned%20on%20and%20service%20could%20continue%20at%20the%20discretion%20of%20the%20crew%2C%20but%20meal%20service%20must%20now%20be%20completely%20paused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlights%20inbound%20(towards%20Singapore)%20from%20Europe%20pass%20over%20a%20patch%20of%20the%20Andaman%20Sea%20known%20for%20turbulence%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Straits%20Times%2C%20which%20cited%20reactions%20from%20crew%20members%20and%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Andaman%20Sea%2C%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20is%20located%20west%20of%20Thailand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20flight%20attendant%20said%20there%20was%20more%20than%20an%20hour%20of%20turbulence%20during%20her%20recent%20three-and-a-half-hour%20flight%20flying%20a%20Singapore-India%20route.%20The%20cabin%20crew%20had%20to%20carry%20out%20meal%20service%20with%20the%20little%20remaining%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20passengers%20don't%20understand%20why%20the%20service%20policy%20change%20is%20important%2C%20and%20rate%20service%20as%20average%20to%20poor%20via%20the%20customer%20feedback%20channel%20after%20flights%20where%20service%20was%20affected%20by%20turbulence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20broadsheet%20quoted%20her%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe're%20stressed%20and%20fatigued%2C%20but%20at%20the%20moment%20there's%20nothing%20we%20can%20do%20except%20continue%20to%20navigate%20our%20work%20under%20the%20given%20circumstances.%E2%80%9D%20A%20flight%20steward%20said%20crew%20members%20have%20had%20to%20make%20adjustments%20%E2%80%9Cby%20doing%20things%20like%20removing%20after-take-off%20drinks%20to%20manage%20the%20time%20we%20have%20for%20meal%20service%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%3A%20%E2%80%9CPassenger%20reactions%20vary%20--%20some%20are%20very%20understanding%2C%20while%20others%20feel%20short-changed.%E2%80%9D%20During%20pre-flight%20briefings%20he%20has%20attended%20since%20the%20incident%2C%20in-flight%20managers%20have%20been%20actively%20checking%20upon%20crew%20members'%20well-being%2C%20the%20flight%20steward%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20counselling%20team%20had%20been%20formed%20to%20support%20cabin%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20crew%20member%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%20might%20be%20more%20stressful%20as%20meal%20service%20may%20be%20affected%2C%20I%20think%20the%20crew%20will%20try%20to%20provide%20the%20same%20service%20standards%20safely.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can't%20fight%20Mother%20Nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20SIA%20crew%20member%20who%20has%20been%20flying%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20adding%20that%20safety%20remains%20the%20crew's%20top%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohn%20Tan%2C%20lead%20professional%20officer%20teaching%20in%20the%20air%20transport%20management%20degree%20programme%20at%20the%20Singapore%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20said%20the%20policy%20change%20%E2%80%9Chighlights%20the%20importance%20of%20adaptability%20in%20aviation%20safety%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrompt%20responses%20are%20necessary%20to%20protect%20passengers%20and%20crew%20effectively.%20Enacting%20policy%20changes%20in%20response%20to%20incidents%20fosters%20a%20culture%20of%20continuous%20safety%20improvement%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Singapore%20daily%20quoted%20Tan%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20task%20of%20balancing%20safety%20and%20service%20quality%20may%20present%20a%20challenge%20for%20SIA%2C%20added%20Tan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20objective%20is%20to%20reduce%20the%20time%20cabin%20crew%20have%20to%20spend%20on%20the%20aisles.%20For%20SIA%2C%20this%20could%20translate%20into%20retraining%20cabin%20crew%20to%20increase%20their%20efficiency%20or%20changing%20the%20way%20services%20are%20delivered%20without%20compromising%20service%20quality.%20And%20the%20option%20to%20restructure%20the%20cabin%20layout%20remains%20a%20possibility%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Shukor%20Yusof%2C%20founder%20of%20aviation%20consultancy%20Endau%20Analytics%2C%20believes%20that%20SIA's%20service%20quality%20will%20not%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20new%20protocol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20was%20arrived%20at%20after%20careful%20consideration%20and%20the%20urgent%20need%20to%2C%20first%20and%20foremost%2C%20prevent%20nasty%20injuries%20for%20passengers%20and%20crew%20in%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Singapore%20daily%20also%20had%20some%20netizens%20suggesting%20that%20passengers%20should%20take%20along%20their%20food%20and%20drinks%20on%20board%20in%20case%20meal%20service%20was%20canned%20due%20to%20turbulence%2C%20especially%20on%20short-%20and%20medium-haul%20flights.%20PY%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717040580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fufhmkdk_singapore-airlines_625x300_24_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsingapore-airlines-comes-up-with-safety-measures-after-deadly-turbulence-57755