at%20his%20stats%20but%20he%20was%20KKR's%20MVP%20even%20before%20the%20season%20got%20underway.%20The%20world%20has%20seen%20his%20talent%20as%20an%20all-rounder%20and%20i'm%20sure%20that%20Narine%20still%20has%20plenty%20of%20to%20give%20to%20KKR%20and%20world%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717039920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcmu29hro_gautam-gambhir_625x300_20_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcan-i-bring-my-girlfriend-to-ipl-gautam-gambhir-reveals-kkr-stars-first-words-5772501%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22KKR%20defeated%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20in%20the%20IPL%202024%20final%20on%20Sunday%20in%20Chennai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcan-i-bring-my-girlfriend-to-ipl-gautam-gambhir-reveals-kkr-stars-first-words-5772501%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcan-i-bring-my-girlfriend-to-ipl-gautam-gambhir-reveals-kkr-stars-first-words-5772501%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcan-i-bring-my-girlfriend-to-ipl-gautam-gambhir-reveals-kkr-stars-first-words-5772501%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Natasa%20works%20out%2C%20plays%20reckless%20love%20amid%20divorce%20rumours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717039884000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110550090%2Cimgsize-84308.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Famid-divorce-rumours-natasa-stankovic-is-spending-time-at-the-gym-bonding-with-her-pet-dog-listening-to-reckless-love-pic-inside%2Farticleshow%2F110550044.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110550044.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENatasa%20Stankovic%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20heading%20for%20a%20divorce%20but%20the%20couple%20has%20remained%20tight%20lipped%20about%20it.%20Natasa's%20post%20amidst%20these%20rumours%20are%20all%20about%20having%20faith%20in%20God%20while%20she%20gets%20her%20positivity%20going%20through%20gym%20activities!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Famid-divorce-rumours-natasa-stankovic-is-spending-time-at-the-gym-bonding-with-her-pet-dog-listening-to-reckless-love-pic-inside%2Farticleshow%2F110550044.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO's%20Backing%2C%20Dogged%20Will%3A%20How%20Chennai%20Start-Up%20Scripted%20Rocket%20History%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAgnikul%20Cosmos%2C%20India's%20private%20space%20start-up%2C%20today%20test-fired%20its%20rocket%20named%20Agnibaan%20SOrTeD%20(Suborbital%20Tech%20Demonstrator)%2C%20which%20is%20powered%20by%20an%20engine%20that%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20is%20still%20trying%20to%20master.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20has%20announced%20that%20the%20Chennai%20based%20start-up%20successfully%20launched%20the%20rocket%20at%207.15%20am.%20ISRO%20chairman%20Mr%20S%20Somanath%20confirmed%20to%20NDTV%20that%20the%20launch%20was%20%26quot%3Bsuccessful%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECongratulations%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAgnikulCosmos%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40AgnikulCosmos%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20successful%20launch%20of%20the%20Agnibaan%20SoRTed-01%20mission%20from%20their%20launch%20pad.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20major%20milestone%2C%20as%20the%20first-ever%20controlled%20flight%20of%20a%20semi-cryogenic%20liquid%20engine%20realized%20through%20additive%20manufacturing.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FINSPACeIND%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40INSPACeIND%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1796009306929738239%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2030%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongratulations%20%40AgnikulCosmos%20for%20the%20successful%20launch%20of%20the%20Agnibaan%20SoRTed-01%20mission%20from%20their%20launch%20pad.%20A%20major%20milestone%2C%20as%20the%20first-ever%20controlled%20flight%20of%20a%20semi-cryogenic%20liquid%20engine%20realized%20through%20additive%20manufacturing%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatya%20R%20Chakravarty%2C%20a%20professor%20from%20IIT%20Madras%20and%20a%20mentor%20for%20Agnikul%2C%20too%2C%20said%20the%20launch%20from%20Sriharikota%20was%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20fifth%20attempt%20to%20launch%20the%20rocket%20after%20four%20launch%20plans%20were%20aborted%20due%20to%20technical%20glitches.%20Rocketry%20is%20not%20for%20the%20faint-hearted%2C%20and%20the%20young%20team%20of%20engineers%20from%20the%20Chennai-based%20start-up%20has%20showed%20remarkable%20patience%20and%20bounced%20back%20every%20time%20a%20glitch%20foiled%20their%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncubated%20at%20IIT-Madras%2C%20this%20was%20the%20first%20test%20flight%20for%20the%20start-up%2C%20founded%20in%202017%20by%20two%20young%20aerospace%20engineers%20with%20a%20dream%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Ba%20place%20where%20people%20learn%20to%20use%20fire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rocket%2C%20which%20weighs%20575%20kg%20and%20is%206.2-metre%20long%2C%20lifted%20off%20from%20Sriharikota%20plunging%20into%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Agnibaan%20SOrTeD%20is%20powered%20by%20a%20semi-cryogenic%20engine%20that%20uses%20commercially%20available%20aviation%20turbine%20fuel%2C%20essentially%20kerosene%20and%20medical%20grade%20liquid%20oxygen%2C%20said%20Moin%20SPM%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Agnikul%20Cosmos%20Private%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20has%20never%20flown%20a%20semi-cryogenic%20engine.%20It%20is%20developing%20a%202000%20kN%20thrust%20semi-cryogenic%20engine%20and%20the%20first%20ignition%20trial%20was%20conducted%20successfully%20on%20May%202.%20So%2C%20the%20Chennai-based%20start-up%20has%20achieved%20what%20no%20other%20Indian%20private%20firm%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgnikul%20has%20demonstrated%20the%20first%20semi-cryogenic%20and%203D%20printed%20engine%20by%20the%20Indian%20private%20sector%2C%20says%20Dr%20Pawan%20Goenka%2C%20a%20mechanical%20engineer%20and%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Space%20Promotion%20and%20Authorisation%20Centre%20(IN-SPACe)%20under%20the%20Centre's%20Department%20of%20Space.%20%26quot%3BThis%20bold%20innovation%20could%20be%20a%20significant%20differentiator%20when%20commercial%20launches%20start%20by%20India's%20start-ups.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrinath%20Ravichandran%2C%20a%20co-founder%20of%20the%20space%20start-up%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20launch%20is%20significant%20since%20it%20is%20India's%20first%20launch%20from%20a%20private%20launchpad%20and%20the%20rocket%20has%20the%20world's%20first%20single%20piece%203D%20printed%20engine%20designed%20and%20built%20indigenously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20tested%20its%20first-ever%203D%20printed%20engine%20in%20ground%20tests%20on%20May%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20launch%2C%20the%20start-up%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BAgnibaan%20SOrTeD%20(Suborbital%20Tech%20Demonstrator)%20is%20a%20single-stage%20launch%20vehicle%20driven%20by%20Agnikul's%20patented%20Agnilet%20engine%20-%20an%20entirely%203D-printed%2C%20single-piece%2C%206%20kN%20semi-cryogenic%20engine.%20Agnibaan%20SOrTeD%20will%20lift%20off%20vertically%20and%20follow%20a%20predetermined%20trajectory.%20The%20trajectory%2C%20manoeuvres%20and%20various%20flight%20events%20that%20will%20occur%20during%20the%20mission%20have%20been%20configured%20to%20validate%20tech%20integral%20to%20the%20success%20of%20our%20upcoming%20orbital%20flights.%20We%20are%20excited%20to%20be%20attempting%20this%20flight%20from%20our%20own%20launch%20pad%20%5Bnamed%20Dhanush%5D%20at%20Sriharikota.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20Agnibaan's%20special%203D%20printed%20engine%20can%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20game-changer%2C%20Mr%20Moin%20told%20NDTV%20that%20it%20is%20a%20single-piece%20equipment%20and%20the%20quality%20testing%20time%20for%20such%20engines%20is%20highly%20reduced%20by%20using%203D%20printing%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engine%20is%20powered%20by%20commercially%20available%20aviation%20turbine%20fuel%20and%20liquid%20oxygen.%20This%20makes%20for%20a%20cheap%20and%20easily%20available%20non-corrosive%20fuel%20which%20can%20be%20sourced%20easily%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20also%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20launch%20rockets%20from%20multiple%20locations%20with%20minimum%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20first%2C%20Agnikul%20has%20got%20the%20go-ahead%20to%20build%20a%20special%20launchpad%20near%20the%20sea%20on%20the%20Sriharikota%20island%20with%20its%20own%20dedicated%20control%20room.%20This%20is%20part%20of%20ISRO%20opening%20up%20its%20facilities%20for%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20for%20Indian%20space%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20the%20first%20controlled%20flight%20of%20a%20rocket%20by%20a%20private%20company%2C%20and%20all%20precautions%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20make%20sure%20nothing%20goes%20amiss.%20If%20things%20go%20awry%2C%20then%20the%20self-destruct%20mechanism%20provided%20by%20ISRO%20can%20be%20activated%20by%20the%20Range%20Safety%20Officer%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Moin%20said%20ahead%20of%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgnikul%20follows%20up%20on%20the%20first%20launch%20by%20an%20Indian%20space%20company%2C%20Skyroot%20Aerospace%20Private%20Limited%2C%20which%20in%202022%20flew%20a%20solid%20fuelled%20sounding%20rocket%20from%20Sriharikota.%20Once%20Agnibaan%20rockets%20become%20operational%2C%20Agnikul%20hopes%20to%20undertake%20launch%20on%20demand%20and%20launch%2030%20to%20300%20kg%20satellites%20into%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20to%20build%20dedicated%2C%20fully%20customisable%20and%20transportable%20launch%20vehicles%20for%20small%20satellites%20to%20Low%20Earth%20Orbits%20(LEO).%20The%20launch%20vehicle%20Agnibaan%20is%20powered%20by%20a%20single-piece%203D-printed%20engine%20that%20can%20be%20made%20in%2072%20hours%20without%20any%20human%20intervention.%20It%20is%20compatible%20with%20the%20mobile%20launch%20pad%20called%20'Dhanush'%20which%20makes%20the%20launch%20location%20agnostic%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20it%20could%20be%20configured%20to%20fly%20with%204%2F5%2F6%2F7%20%5Bengines%5D%20which%20makes%20the%20launch%20cost%20the%20same%20across%20the%20spectrum%20of%20mass%20-%2030%20kg%20-%20300%20kg%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgnikul%20has%20already%20attracted%20an%20investment%20of%2040%20million%20dollars%20and%20has%20a%20team%20of%20250%20members.%20%26quot%3BThe%20average%20age%20of%20employees%20at%20Agnikul%20is%2023%20years%20and%20all%20are%20fired%20up%20to%20innovate%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mr%20Moin%2C%20underscoring%20that%20India%20can%20become%20a%20hub%20for%20small%20satellite%20launches%20as%20more%20and%20more%20global%20companies%20are%20opting%20for%20constellations%20of%20satellites%20placed%20in%20low%20earth%20orbits.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717039620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmnvlnmc_agnikul_625x300_30_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisros-backing-dogged-will-how-chennai-start-u