-99-wipeouts-in-past%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2007%3A%20Farnsworth%20becomes%20CEO%20of%20Purple%20Beverage%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221994%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ted%20Farnsworth%20standing%20next%20to%20Mariano%20Rivera%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66561f29a961b37edf3a73aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221496%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20Ted%20Farnsworth%20and%20Mariano%20Rivera.%3Cp%3EGary%20Gershoff%2FWireImage%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFarnsworth's%20failure%20with%20XStream%20didn't%20stop%20him%20from%20trying%20another%20venture%20in%20the%20drink%20space.%20He%20became%20the%20CEO%20of%20Purple%20Beverage%20Co.%2C%20touting%20an%20antioxidant-rich%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20for%20Purple%20Bev%20went%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2017-10-30%2Fman-behind-1-151-stock-rally-has-overseen-99-wipeouts-in-past%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20as%20%243.24%20in%20April%202008%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thanks%20partly%20to%20Farnsworth%20landing%20celebrity%20spokespeople%20like%20Chaka%20Khan%20and%20New%20York%20Yankees%20Hall%20of%20Fame%20pitcher%20Mariano%20Rivera.%20But%20by%20the%20time%20he%20resigned%20a%20year%20later%2C%20the%20stock%20had%20plummeted%20by%2099%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2012%3A%20He%20oversees%20a%20vitamin%20company%20that%20flatlines%20within%20a%20year%20and%20is%20sued%20by%20FedEx%3Cp%3EFarnsworth%20became%20the%20chairman%20of%20LTS%20Nutraceuticals%20Inc.%2C%20a%20multilevel-marketing%20vitamin%20company.%20In%202011%2C%20it%20traded%20as%20high%20as%20%244.85.%20But%20by%202012%2C%20with%20Farnsworth%20running%20things%2C%20the%20stock%20fell%2099%25.%20It's%20unclear%20when%20he%20left%20the%20company%20because%20it%20didn't%20make%20periodic%20regulatory%20filings%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2017-10-30%2Fman-behind-1-151-stock-rally-has-overseen-99-wipeouts-in-past%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20FedEx%20sued%20the%20vitamin%20company%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20owed%20%2426%2C000.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.miamiherald.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Farticle213952134.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Miami%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20judge%20ruled%20in%20FedEx's%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2016%3A%20Farnsworth%E2%80%99s%20Zone%20Technologies%20merges%20with%20HMNY%20to%20become%20publicly%20listed%20on%20the%20Nasdaq%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20decade%20after%20Farmbid%2C%20Farnsworth%20went%20back%20into%20the%20tech%20space%20with%20an%20app%20called%20RedZone%20Maps%20(through%20a%20company%20called%20Zone%20Technologies).%20The%20app%20flagged%20where%20crimes%20were%20being%20reported%20in%20a%20user's%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20Zone%20Technologies%20merged%20with%20Helios%20and%20Matheson%20to%20become%20publicly%20listed%20on%20the%20Nasdaq.%20That%20same%20year%2C%20Farnsworth%20was%20named%20CEO%20of%20HMNY.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2017%3A%20HMNY%20acquires%20a%20majority%20stake%20in%20MoviePass%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MoviePass%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5b62348804f16230008b4892%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHollis%20Johnson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20birth%20in%202011%2C%20MoviePass%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20a%20monthly%20subscription%20price%20that%20attracted%20moviegoers%20and%20would%20make%20a%20profit.%20By%202017%2C%20the%20company%20was%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20running%20out%20of%20money%20when%20Farnsworth%20got%20connected%20with%20MoviePass'%20then-CEO%2C%20Mitch%20Lowe.%20A%20deal%20was%20made%20for%20HMNY%20to%20take%20a%20majority%20stake%20in%20MoviePass.%20By%20that%20summer%2C%20Farnsworth%20and%20Lowe%20dropped%20the%20price%20to%20%2410%20a%20month%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20is%20history.%20With%20a%20huge%20rise%20in%20subscribers%20for%20MoviePass%2C%20the%20HMNY%20stock%20initially%20soared.%20But%20by%202020%2C%20MoviePass%20and%20HMNY%20went%20bankrupt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20bankruptcy%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20was%20under%20pending%20investigations%20by%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%2C%20SEC%2C%20four%20California%20district%20attorneys%2C%20and%20the%20New%20York%20attorney%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Farnsworth%20and%20Lowe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoviepass-executives-settle-ftc-blocking-subscribers-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esettled%20with%20the%20FTC%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reached%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoviepass-execs-reach-400000-settlement-with-california-district-attorneys-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24400%2C000%20settlement%20with%20the%20California%20district%20attorneys%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2021%3A%20Less%20than%20a%20year%20after%20MoviePass'%20bankruptcy%2C%20Farnsworth%20founds%20Zash%20Global%20Media%20and%20Entertainment%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20MoviePass'%20bankruptcy%2C%20Farnsworth%20quickly%20landed%20back%20on%20his%20feet%20by%20starting%20a%20media%20company%20called%20Zash%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year.%20He%20later%20merged%20it%20with%20the%20publicly%20traded%20company%20Vinco%20Ventures.%20He%20acquired%20a%20TikTok%20rival%20called%20Lomotif%20and%20even%20tried%20(unsuccessfully)%20to%20buy%20the%20National%20Enquirer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202022%2C%20Vinco%20stock%20had%20cratered%20and%20is%20now%20worth%20less%20than%20one%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-moviepass-ex-chairman-tiktok-rival-collapsed-cost-investors-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Farnsworth's%20business%20tactics%20while%20at%20Zash.%20They%20mirror%20how%20he%20operated%20at%20MoviePass%20and%20some%20other%20ventures%20over%20the%20decades%3A%20Get%20involved%20with%20a%20publicly%20traded%20company%2C%20help%20raise%20funding%20from%20his%20finance%20connections%20at%20favorable%20terms%20for%20them%2C%20drive%20up%20the%20company's%20stock%20with%20splashy%20announcements%2C%20and%20leave%20retail%20investors%20with%20big%20losses%20when%20the%20stock%20crashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2022%3A%20Farnsworth%20is%20charged%20with%20securities%20fraud%20related%20to%20his%20time%20at%20MoviePass%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MoviePass%20CEO%20Mitch%20Lowe%20and%20Helios%20and%20Matheson%20Chief%20Executive%20Ted%20Farnsworth.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5afb8ade42e1cc328858d703%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E(L-R)%20MoviePass%20CEO%20Mitch%20Lowe%20and%20Helios%20and%20Matheson%20Chief%20Executive%20Ted%20Farnsworth.%3Cp%3EMoviePass%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Farnsworth%20and%20Lowe%20were%20each%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-ceo-of-moviepass-charged-in-securities-fraud-case-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echarged%20with%20one%20count%20of%20securities%20fraud%20and%20three%20counts%20of%20wire%20fraud%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20alleged%20the%20two%20%26quot%3Bengaged%20in%20a%20scheme%20to%20defraud%20investors%20through%20materially%20false%20and%20misleading%20representations%20relating%20to%20HMNY%20and%20MoviePass's%20business%20and%20operations%20to%20artificiall