urity%20on%20high%20alert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20that%20has%20gone%20global%2C%20the%20terror%20group%20is%20%26quot%3Bcalling%20for%20that%20'Lone%20Wolf'%20to%20act%20out%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Patrick%20Ryder%2C%20the%20Police%20Commissioner%20of%20Nassau%20County%20where%20the%20match%20is%20scheduled%20for%20June%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLone%20Wolves%26quot%3B%20are%20members%20or%20sympathisers%20of%20terrorist%20organisations%20who%20take%20cues%20from%20the%20organisations%20and%20operate%20independently%20by%20themselves%20making%20it%20more%20difficult%20to%20track%20them%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20New%20York%20Governor%20Kathy%20Hochul%20said%20that%20she%20has%20%26quot%3Bdirected%20the%20New%20York%20State%20Police%20to%20engage%20in%20elevated%20security%20measures%2C%20including%20an%20increased%20law%20enforcement%20presence%2C%20advanced%20surveillance%2C%20and%20thorough%20screening%20processes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBruce%20Blakeman%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Nassau%20County%20bordering%20New%20York%20City%2C%20said%20at%20a%20news%20conference%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20are%20on%20top%20of%20every%20situation%20that%20could%20potentially%20arise.%20Now%20to%20that%20end%2C%20we%20have%20taken%20many%20many%20precautions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20police%20officers%20will%20be%20mobilised%20at%20the%20cricket%20stadium%20at%20Eisenhower%20Park%2C%20Ryder%20said%20at%20the%20news%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20go%20to%20every%20fine%20detail%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20security%20and%20safety%20of%20the%20residents%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20there%20had%20been%20some%20ambiguity%20about%20the%20level%20of%20the%20threat%20posted%20in%20a%20chat%20group%20by%20ISIS-Khorasan%2C%20the%20offshoot%20of%20the%20Islamic%20State%20terrorist%20organisation%20operating%20in%20South%20and%20Central%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20news%20conference%20by%20Nassau%20officials%2C%20Hochul%20had%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20credible%20public%20safety%20threat%20at%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20monitor%20the%20situation%20closely.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20administration%20has%20been%20working%20for%20months%20with%20federal%20law%20enforcement%20and%20Nassau%20County%20to%20ensure%20New%20Yorkers%20and%20visitors%20are%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlakeman%20said%20at%20the%20news%20conference%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20take%20every%20threat%20seriously.%20There%20are%20the%20same%20procedures%20for%20every%20threat.%20We%20don't%20minimise%20threats.%20We%20track%20down%20all%20of%20our%20leads.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERyder%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20a%20game%20and%20a%20crowd%20as%20big%20as%20this%2C%20everything%20is%20credible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20they%20had%20received%20threats%20starting%20in%20April%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20it%20was%20a%20global%20and%20international%20style%20threat%20from%20what's%20called%20ISIS-K%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20it%20got%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20specific%20towards%20the%20actual%20game%20of%20India%20versus%20Pakistan%20but%20did%20not%20name%20the%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20yesterday%2C%20you%20all%20saw%20the%20video%20that%20went%20global%2C%20and%20they%20are%20calling%20for%20that%20'Lone%20Wolf'%20to%20act%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20referring%20to%20a%20video%20with%20%26quot%3Ban%20image%20of%20the%20cricket%20stadium%20at%20Eisenhower%20Park%20in%20Nassau%20County%20with%20drones%20flying%20over%20it%20showing%20the%20date%2C%20%26quot%3B9%2F6%2F2024%26quot%3B%2C%20when%20the%20India-Pakistan%20match%2C%20that%20was%20posted%20by%20ISIS-K%20on%20a%20British%20chat%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20display%20of%20drones%20as%20attack%20vehicles%2C%20NBC%20New%20York%20TV%20reported%20that%20county%20officials%20%26quot%3Bsay%20they've%20requested%20the%20FAA%20(Federal%20Aviation%20Administration)%20to%20make%20Eisenhower%20Park%20a%20no-fly%20zone%20for%20drones%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISIS-K%20has%20carried%20out%20attacks%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20has%20threatened%20terror%20strikes%20on%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20ISIS-K%20terrorists%20attacked%20a%20concert%20hall%20in%20Moscow%20killing%20about%20130%20people%20adding%20gravity%20to%20the%20latest%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Cup%20Cricket%20stadium%2C%20which%20has%20a%2030%2C000-capacity%2C%20was%20built%20specially%20for%20the%20tournament%20and%20will%20share%20the%20fixtures%20in%20the%20US%20with%20the%20arena%20in%20Dallas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20kick%20off%20on%20June%201%20with%20an%20exhibition%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20and%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20regular%20tournament%20matches%20starting%20on%20June%203%2C%20pitching%20India%20against%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20and%20running%20till%20June%2012%20with%20an%20India%20vs%20US%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENBC%20New%20York%20TV%20said%20that%20the%20security%20preparations%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20event%20were%20the%20largest%20that%20Nassau%20County%20has%20undertaken%20and%20it%20is%20being%20treated%20on%20par%20with%20presidential%20debates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20safety%20precautions%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLocal%20hospitals%20also%20involved%20just%20in%20case%20they're%20needed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20newspaper%20Express%20first%20reported%20on%20the%20threat%2C%20which%20it%20said%20was%20also%20directed%20against%20sporting%20venues%20in%20Europe%2C%20including%20the%20Wembley%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20ISIS%20%26quot%3Bfollowers%20are%20encouraged%20to%20target%20major%20events%26quot%3B%20including%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20also%20extensive%20discussions%20on%20the%20forum%20as%20to%20how%20the%20terror%20group%20should%20use%20drones%20laden%20with%20explosives%20to%20murder%20civilians%20at%20major%20sporting%20events%20across%20Europe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Express%20said%20of%20the%20postings%20on%20a%20chat%20group%20posted%20on%20the%20British%20website%20Matrix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Express%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BChat%20room%20members%20who%20shared%20the%20stadium%20threats%20listed%20their%20terror%20skills%2C%20including%20firing%20AK-47%20rifles%2C%20and%20discussed%20sums%20of%20money%20in%20pound%20Sterling%2C%20suggesting%20some%20might%20be%20based%20in%20Britain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717032180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-12%2Fcfdbgnbg_cricket-stadium-generic-twitter_625x300_05_December_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisis-linked-outfit-khorasan-threatens-terror-attack-on-india-pak-t20-world-cup-match-in-us-new-york-5774982%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ISIS-K%20has%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3BLone%20Wolf%26quot%3B%20attack%20on%20the%20India-Pakistan%20World%20Cup%20Cricket%20match%20here%20next%20month%2C%20a%20top%20police%20official%20has%20warned%20while%20putting%20security%20on%20high%20alert.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisis-linked-outfit-khorasan-threatens-terror-attack-on-india-pak-t20-world-cup-match-in-us-new-york-5774982%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisis-linked-outfit-khorasan-threatens-terror-attack-on-india-pak-t20-world-cu