e%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmkbhd-fisker-ocean-review-marques-brownlee-video-tiktok-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFisker%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20another%20round%20of%20layoffs%20during%20an%20all-hands%20meeting%20Wednesday%20morning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Henrik%20Fisker%20said%20he%20wasn't%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20decision%2C%20sources%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFisker%20recently%20appointed%20a%20chief%20restructuring%20officer%20who%20was%20given%20sole%20authority%20over%20some%20of%20the%20company's%20financial%20decision-making.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHenrik%20Fisker%20had%20grim%20news%20for%20his%20staff%20when%20they%20logged%20on%20to%20a%20short%20all-hands%20meeting%20Wednesday%20morning.%20The%20electric%20carmaker%20was%20implementing%20yet%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffisker-summer-layoffs-employees-job-cuts-2024-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520embattled%2520electric%252Dvehicle%2520startup%2Ccut%252015%2525%2520of%2520its%2520staff.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eround%20of%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20employees%20who%20attended%20the%20meeting%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20CEO%20and%20founder%20attempted%20to%20shift%20responsibility%20for%20the%20latest%20staff%20cuts%2C%20frustrating%20some%20staff%20who%20felt%20he%20was%20failing%20to%20take%20accountability%20for%20how%20the%20company%20had%20gotten%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHenrik%20Fisker%20told%20employees%20he%20had%20not%20been%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20decision%20to%20cut%20staff%20and%20instead%20said%20the%20choice%20to%20further%20reduce%20the%20company's%20workforce%20was%20made%20by%20chief%20restructuring%20officer%20John%20DiDonato%2C%20two%20employees%20who%20attended%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiDonato%2C%20the%20restructuring%20officer%2C%20is%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20Huron%20Consulting%20Group%20and%20was%20brought%20in%20to%20help%20Fisker%20in%20April.%20Fisker%20was%20required%20to%20install%20a%20chief%20restructuring%20officer%20last%20month%20after%20the%20company%20missed%20an%20interest%20payment%20to%20an%20unnamed%20institutional%20investor%20and%20noteholder.%20The%20agreement%20gave%20the%20CRO%2C%20who%20reports%20directly%20to%20the%20company's%20recently%20established%20transaction%20committee%2C%20%26quot%3Bsole%20authority%26quot%3B%20over%20decision-making%20related%20to%20a%20potential%20sale%20of%20the%20company%20and%20%26quot%3Boversight%20of%20cash%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20an%20April%2016%20filing%20with%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20general%20gist%20of%20the%20meeting%20was%20Henrik%20was%20saying%20'These%20are%20not%20my%20layoffs%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20worker%2C%20who%20witnessed%20the%20meeting%20and%20later%20found%20out%20that%20their%20role%20had%20been%20eliminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20dozens%20of%20workers%20found%20out%20they'd%20been%20impacted%20by%20the%20cut%20when%20they%20lost%20access%20to%20the%20company's%20internal%20systems%2C%20two%20workers%20who%20lost%20their%20jobs%20as%20part%20of%20the%20cuts%20told%20BI.%20The%20employees%20later%20received%20an%20email%20from%20human%20resources%20notifying%20them%20they'd%20been%20impacted%20by%20the%20cuts%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20one%20Fisker%20employee%20took%20to%20the%20company's%20internal%20Microsoft%20Teams%20channel%20to%20criticize%20Henrik%20Fisker's%20comments%2C%20according%20to%20a%20screenshot%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20not%20one%20time%20taken%20responsibility%20for%20what's%20going%20on%20at%20Fisker%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20wrote%20in%20the%20Teams%20chat%2C%20according%20to%20the%20screenshot.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20here%20for%2