pects%20profit%20margins%20for%20the%20current%20quarter%20to%20be%201%25%20lower%20than%20it%20had%20predicted%20in%20April.%20In%20addition%2C%20American%20expects%20second-quarter%20revenue%20to%20be%20as%20much%20as%206%25%20lower%20than%20the%20same%20period%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaja%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20company%20in%202004%20and%20took%20over%20as%20CCO%20in%202022%2C%20will%20officially%20leave%20the%20company%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20American%20Airlines%20fell%20more%20than%2013%25%20in%20trading%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-airlines-ceo-admits-ticket-sales-strategy-change-mistake-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717018570000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66579f98d0b8e1c832ca1565%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-airlines-ceo-admits-ticket-sales-strategy-change-mistake-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22American%20Airlines%20lowered%20its%20earnings%20outlook%20for%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%202024%20and%20announced%20the%20departure%20of%20Chief%20Commercial%20Officer%20Vasu%20Raja.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bzhang%40businessinsider.com%20(Benjamin%20Zhang)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A128%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-airlines-ceo-admits-ticket-sales-strategy-change-mistake-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20worked%20hard%20to%20clean%20up%20my%20finances%20in%20my%2030s%2C%20but%20a%20financial%20planner%20says%20I'm%20still%20making%205%20expensive%20mistakes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-mistakes-financial-planner-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaid%20non-client%20promotion%3A%20Affiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting-rating-methodology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20investing%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222921%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jen%20Glantz%20outside%20with%20microphone%20and%20headphones%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6384de39785afd00189bf255%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221460%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Jen%20Glantz.%3Cp%3EDaphne%20Youree%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20made%20a%20ton%20of%20money%20mistakes%20in%20my%2020s%20and%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20clean%20things%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20finally%20sat%20down%20with%20a%20financial%20planner%2C%20and%20he%20pointed%20out%20five%20mistakes%20I'm%20still%20making.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20have%20too%20much%20cash%20in%20savings%2C%20poor%20tax%20diversification%2C%20too%20many%20single%20stocks%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20before%20I%20turned%2030%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20get%20serious%20about%20my%20finances.%20I%20had%20spent%20most%20of%20my%2020s%20making%20all%20kinds%20of%20money%20mistakes%20(from%20not%20saving%20for%20retirement%20to%20racking%20up%20credit%20card%20debt).%20I%20was%20eager%20to%20approach%20a%20new%20decade%20of%20my%20life%20with%20my%20finances%20in%20a%20strategic%20place%20so%20I%20could%20meet%20the%20big%20goals%20I%20had%20for%20my%20future%2C%20like%20retiring%20early%20and%20buying%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20do%20first%2C%20so%20I%20did%20anything%20I%20could%20to%20tighten%20my%20spending%20and%20start%20investing.%20Since%20I%20never%20worked%20one-on-one%20with%20a%20financial%20professional%2C%20I%20always%20wondered%20if%20I%20was%20making%20any%20glaring%20mistakes.%20It%20turns%20out%20I%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-find-financial-advisor%5C%22%3Efind%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20sat%20down%20with%20Adam%20Scherer%2C%20a%20financial%20planner%20and%20president%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenbeatfinancial.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreenbeat%20Financial%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20review%20every%20inch%20of%20my%20financial%20portfolio%20to%20not%20only%20identify%20the%20mistakes%20I'm%20making%20but%20also%20make%20a%20game%20plan%20for%20how%20I%20can%20start%20fixing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20I%20have%20too%20much%20cash%20in%20a%20savings%20account%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20mistake%20I%20knew%20Scherer%20would%20bring%20up%20is%20a%20mistake%20I've%20knowingly%20made%20for%20years.%20More%20than%20half%20of%20my%20financial%20portfolio%20is%20cash%20that's%20just%20sitting%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3Esavings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20making%20this%20mistake%20because%20I'm%20not%20sure%20what%20else%20to%20do%20with%20that%20money%20and%20I'm%20scared%20to%20lose%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScherer%20said%20it's%20great%20to%20have%20cash%20on%20hand%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-an-emergency-fund%5C%22%3Eemergency%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%C2%A0good%20rule%20of%20thumb%20is%20that%20a%20couple%20should%20have%20between%20six%20and%20nine%20months%20of%20fixed%20and%20variable%20expenses%20in%20their%20cash%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20how%20can%20I%20fix%20this%20mistake%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScherer%20says%20that%2C%20first%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20assess%20my%20risk%20tolerance%2C%20then%20get%20clarity%20on%20when%20I'd%20want%20to%20access%20that%20money%20in%20the%20future%20(whether%20it's%20for%20retirement%20in%2020%20years%20or%20to%20buy%20a%20house%20in%20five%20years).%20Once%20I%20know%20the%20answers%20to%20those%20two%20things%2C%20I%20can%20consider%20putting%20that%20money%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-retirement-plans%5C%22%3Eretirement%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20(through%20index%20or%20mutual%20funds)%2C%20or%20investing%20in%20real%20estate%20(both%20directly%20by%20purchasing%20real%20estate%20or%20through%20a%20REIT%2C%20which%20allows%20you%20to%20invest%20in%20real%20estate%20properties%20without%20buying%20one%20yourself).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20My%20risk%20balance%20might%20be%20wrong%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20after%20many%20friends%20advised%20me%20to%20do%20this%2C%20I%20opened%20up%20an%20investment%20portfolio%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-robo-advisors%5C%22%3Erobo-advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20automatically%20manages%20your%20money%20for%20you.%20All%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20set%20your%20risk%20tolerance%20and%20they%20do%20the%20rest.%20Without%20much%20thought%2C%20I%20did%20what%20my%20friends%20did%20and%20set%20that%20tolerance%20to%20be%2090%25%20stocks%20and%2010%25%20bonds%2C%20making%20this%20allocation%20very%20risky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScherer%20says%20that%20because%20I'm%20a%20bit%20scared%20of%20risk%20right%20now%20and%20unsure%20of%20my%20financial%20goals%2C%20it%20might%20make%20more%20sense%20to%20dial%20that%20down%20from%2090%2F10%20to%2080%25%20stock%20and%2020%25%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20idea%20right%20now%20that%20your%20money%20is%2090%25%20in%20risky%20assets%20and%20only%2010%25%20in%20something%20that's%20safe%20makes%20you%20uneasy%2C%20it's%20OK%20to%20adjust%20this%20to%20be%20in%20a%20more%20comfortable%20place%20as%20you%20seek%20advice%20and%20guidance%20from%20a%20professional%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Scherer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20I%20have%20too%20many%20random%20individual%20stocks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20confessed%20to%20Scherer%20that%2C%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20put%20a%20little%20money%20into%20many%20individual%20stocks%20without%20much%20research%20or%20thought.%20What%20Scherer%20noticed%20was%20that%20most%20of%20those%20stocks%20fell%20in%20one%20sector%20(tech%2C%20media%2C%20and%20telecom)%2C%20and%20having%20a%20portfolio%20that%20was%20heavily%20weighted%20in%20one%20industry%20can%20be%20risky%20and%20not%20strategic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScherer%20recommends%20diversifying%20across%20different%20sectors%20since%20these%20sectors%20are%20more%20in%20tandem%20at%20different%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20are%20my%20options%3F%20Scherer%20said%20I%20can%20sell%20my%20current%20individual%20stocks%20and%20use%20that%20money%20to%20invest%20in%20stocks%20across%20different%20sectors%2C%20or%20I%20can%20go%20broader%20and%20buy%20sector-focused%20ETFs%20to%20have%20a%20fully%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-diversification%5C%22%3Ediversified%20portfolio%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wondered%20if%20this%20meant%20I%20should%20ensure%20I'm%20investing%20equal%20amounts%20of%20money%20in%20each%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20depends%20on%20the%20rate%20of%20return%20you're%20looking%20to%20generate%2C%20where%20we%20are%20in%20the%20buzz%20cycle%2C%20where%20we're%20heading%2C%20and%20more%20factors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scherer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E4.%20I%20need%20more%20tax%20diversification%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20Scherer%20said%20was%20missing%20from%20my%20portfolio%20was%20tax%20diversification.%20He%20explained%20that%20there%20are%20three%20tax%20buckets%3A%20taxable%20assets%20(such%20as%20money%20in%20a%20taxable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-online-brokerage%5C%22%3Ebrokerage%20account%3C%2Fa%3E)%3B%20tax-deferred%20(where%20the%20money%20is%20taxed%20down%20the%20line%2C%20like%20my%20SEP%20IRA)%3B%20and%20tax-free%20(where%20the%20money%20isn't%20taxed%2C%20like%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-roth-ira%5C%22%3ERoth%20IRA%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScherer%20said%20I'd%20have%20challenges%20with%20a%20Roth%20IRA%20because%20I%20potentially%20make%20too%20much%20money%20to%20contribute%20to%20one%2C%20and%20I'm%20married%20filing%20separately%20from%20my%20spouse%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20qualify%20for%20the%20higher%20limit.%20However%2C%20he%20did%20mention%20a%20workaround.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20still%20execute%20a%20backdoor%20Roth%20IRA%20strategy%20to%20get%20more%20investments%20into%20your%20'tax-free'%20investment%20bucket%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scherer.%20%26quot%3BTo%20do%20so%2C%20you'd%20open%20a%20traditional%20IRA%20account%20and%20a%20Roth%20IRA%20account%2C%20then%20make%20'nondeductible%20traditional%20IRA%20contributions'%20and%20convert%20the%20funds%20over%20to%20the%20Roth%20IRA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20aren't%20protecting%20each%20other%20financially%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20I%20mentioned%20to%20Scherer%20at%20the%20end%20of%20our%20meeting%20was%20that%20I%20recently%20got%20married.%20Even%20though%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20keep%20most%20of%20our%20finances%20separate%20and%20don't%20file%20taxes%20together%2C%20I%20wondered%20if%20there%20was%20anything%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20should%20do%20with%20our%20finances%20now%20that%20we've%20tied%20the%20knot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScherer%20said%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20is%20make%20each%20other%20beneficiaries%20on%20your%20different%20accounts%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scherer.%20%26quot%3BIf%20an%20asset's%20contract%20(like%20your%20retirement%20account%2C%20savings%20account%2C%20investment%20portfolio)%20has%20a%20beneficiary%2C%20you%20can%20bypass%20the%20long%20process%20of%20having%20your%20assets%20in%20probate%20with%20the%20court.%20Instead%2C%20your%20assets%20will%20transfer%20automatically%20to%20that%20person%2C%20saving%20time%20and%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20thing%20Scherer%20mentioned%20was%20that%20now%20that%20we're%20married%2C%20we%20should%20consider%20getting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-life-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Elife%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20both%20have%20a%20life%20insurance%20policy%20in%20place%2C%20it%20can%20ensure%20the%20other%20person%20is%20able%20to%20pay%20for%20some%20debts%20and%20maintain%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20they%20are%20accustomed%20to%20if%20their%20partner%20passes%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Scherer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20that%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAdvisor%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20April%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-mistakes-financial-planner-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717018381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F625f0f774f524b00194d418d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-mistakes-financial-planner-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jen%20Glantz%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20clean%20up%20her%20finances%20in%20her%2030s%2C%20but%20she's%20been%20too%20focused%20slashing%20her%20spending%20and%20investing%20without%20a%20plan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jen%20Glantz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-mistakes-financial-planner-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20is%20developing%20systems%20to%20hunt%20US%20submarines%20from%20the%20air%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22China's%20navy%20wants%20aircrews%20to%20play%20a%20larger%20role%20in%20hunting%20enemy%20submarines.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665754ded0b8e1c832c9cd6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChina's%20navy%20wants%20aircrews%20to%20play%20a%20larger%20role%20in%20hunting%20enemy%20submarines.%3Cp%3ELi%20Hao%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChina%20is%20developing%20sensors%20to%20hunt%20enemy%20submarines%20from%20aircraft.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERecent%20patents%20show%20a%20focus%20on%20magnetic%20detection%20and%20improved%20sonobuoys.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20capabilities%20are%20critical%20for%20China%20to%20guard%20its%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20two%20experts%20said.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20is%20developing%20new%20systems%20to%20hunt%20the%20US%20nuclear-powered%20submarines%20that%20could%20threaten%20a%20Chinese%20invasion%20of%20Taiwan%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chinese%20navy%20views%20anti-submarine%20warfare%2C%20or%20ASW%2C%20as%20essential%20to%20any%20successful%20amphibious%20operation%20and%20intends%20to%20use%20its%20aircraft%20to%20protect%20a%20flotilla%20from%20submarine%20attack%20by%20the%20US%20or%20Japan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PLAN%20%5BPeople's%20Liberation%20Army%20Navy%5D%20clearly%20views%20fixed-wing%20and%20vertical%20lift%20ASW%20capabilities%20as%20a%20crucial%20component%20necessary%20for%20any%20of%20its%20amphibious%20based%20contingencies%2C%20be%20that%20a%20seizure%20of%20an%20island%20or%20reef%2C%20or%20the%20successful%20implementation%20of%20a%20Joint%20Island%20Landing%20Campaign%20against%20Taiwan%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Eli%20Tirk%20and%20Daniel%20Salisbury%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigital-commons.usnwc.edu%2Fcgi%2Fviewcontent.cgi%3Farticle%3D1038%26context%3Dcmsi-maritime-reports%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20China%20Maritime%20Studies%20Institute%20at%20the%20Naval%20War%20College.%20%26quot%3BASW%20capabilities%20would%20be%20crucial%20for%20safeguarding%20high%20value%20surface%20assets%20such%20as%20carriers%20or%20an%20amphibious%20landing%20group%2C%20protecting%20them%20as%20they%20are%20in%20port%20embarking%20forces%2C%20sanitizing%20the%20operational%20area%20of%20enemy%20submarines%2C%20and%20escorting%20these%20assets%20on%20their%20way%20to%20staging%20areas%20and%20operational%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20significant%20is%20that%20Chinese%20airborne%20sub%20hunters%20are%20tasked%20with%20protecting%20Chinese%20ballistic%20missile%20submarines%20as%20they%20sail%20to%20their%20patrol%20and%20launch%20locations.%20%26quot%3BThe%20PLAN%20clearly%20views%20fixed-wing%20ASW%20as%20an%20important%20enabler%20of%20its%20at-sea%20nuclear%20deterrent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chinese%20navy's%20current%20fixed-wing%20anti-submarine%20aircraft%20is%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.navalnews.com%2Fnaval-news%2F2019%2F04%2Fnew-details-on-chinas-kq-200-maritime-patrol-aircraft%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKQ-200%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20four-engine%20turboprop%20aircraft%20that%20is%20China's%20equivalent%20of%20the%20US%20Navy's%20P-8%20Poseidon.%20The%20PLAN%20has%20about%2020%20KQ-200s%2C%20which%20have%20a%20range%20of%20about%203%2C000%20miles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20like%20the%20US%20Navy%2C%20China's%20submarine%20force%20tends%20to%20be%20secretive.%20But%20by%20examining%20open-source%20literature%2C%20Tirk%20and%20Salisbury%20were%20able%20to%20discern%20the%20efforts%20China%20is%20making%20in%20anti-submarine%20warfare%2C%20including%20patents%20filed%20by%20Chinese%20researchers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20state-owned%20China%20Electronics%20Technology%20Group%20Corporation%20filed%20a%20patent%20in%202020%20for%20improved%20magnetic%20anomaly%20detection%20(MAD)%2C%20a%20technology%20first%20used%20in%20World%20War%20II%20to%20detect%20subs%20by%20the%20effect%20of%20these%20big%20metal%20objects%20on%20the%20Earth's%20magnetic%20field.%20It's%20a%20useful%20but%20limited%20system%20that%20usually%20requires%20the%20aircraft%20to%20be%20flying%20within%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cae.com%2Fmedia%2Fmedia-center%2Fdocuments%2Fdatasheet.MAD-XR.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eless%20than%20a%20mile%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20target%2C%20and%20can%20only%20detect%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20sub%20rather%20than%20its%20course%20%E2%80%94%20which%20means%20a%20positive%20hit%20must%20be%20followed%20by%20laying%20a%20web%20of%20other%20sensors%20to%20be%20able%20to%20target%20the%20lurking%20submarine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChinese%20scientists%20want%20to%20use%20highly%20sensitive%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fphysicsworld.com%2Fa%2Fatomic-magnetometer-is-most-sensitive-yet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eatomic%20magnetometers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20use%20lasers%20to%20detect%20changes%20in%20the%20energy%20levels%20between%20atoms%20caused%20by%20fluctuations%20in%20a%20magnetic%20field.%20CETC's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpatents-google-com.translate.goog%2Fpatent%2FCN206546425U%2Fzh%3F_x_tr_sl%3Dauto%26_x_tr_tl%3Den%26_x_tr_hl%3Den-US%26_x_tr_hist%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epatent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20for%20technology%20that%20would%20%26quot%3Benable%20an%20atomic%20magnetometer%20to%20sense%20the%20direction%20of%20a%20target%20rather%20than%20just%20its%20existence%2C%26quot%3B%20Tirk%20and%20Salisbury%20noted.%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20filing%2C%20previous%20research%20on%20highly-sensitive%20atomic%20magnetometers%20had%20focused%20on%20scalar%20results%20(i.e.%20only%20the%20magnitude%20of%20a%20target's%20magnetic%20field)%2C%20but%20could%20not%20provide%20vectors%20(i.e.%20magnitude%20and%20direction).%20MAD%20is%20already%20a%20shorter-range%20capability%20usually%20used%20for%20more%20precise%20positioning%20after%20other%20sensors%20have%20provided%20a%20rough%20search%20area%2C%20but%20any%20additional%20information%20could%20potentially%20give%20operators%20an%20edge%20during%20search%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20naval%20aircrewman%20checks%20sonobouys%20loaded%20onto%20a%20MH-60R%20Sea%20Hawk%20helicopter.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665756bfcc442a2f676bcdca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221422%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20naval%20aircrewman%20checks%20sonobouys%20loaded%20onto%20a%20MH-60R%20Sea%20Hawk%20helicopter.%3Cp%3EMC1%20Deanna%20C.%20Gonzales%2FUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%202022%20patent%20by%20Aviation%20Industry%20Corporation%20of%20China%20calls%20for%20a%20new%20system%20to%20operate%20sonobuoys%2C%20which%20are%20floating%20canisters%2C%20dropped%20by%20planes%20and%20ships%2C%20that%20detect%20subs%20by%20emitting%20active%20sonar%20signals%20or%20by%20passive%20sensors%20that%20detect%20the%20noise%20of%20a%20submarine.%20Current%20Chinese%20sonobuoys%20require%20%26quot%3Ba%20complicated%20and%20labor-intensive%20series%20of%20manual%20button%20presses%20to%20configure%20sonobuoy%20parameters%20such%20as%20radio%20working%20frequency%2C%20working%20depth%2C%20working%20time%2C%20and%20pulse%20form%20to%20fit%20maritime%20conditions%20before%20deployment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20parameters%20aren't%20displayed%20on%20the%20sonobuoy%20control%20system.%20%26quot%3BThis%20means%20the%20display%20and%20control%20system%20is%20unaware%20of%20whether%20a%20sonobuoy%20is%20on%20the%20rack%20or%20has%20been%20launched%2C%20what%20type%20of%20sonobuoys%20have%20been%20launched%2C%20or%20the%20parameters%20of%20any%20launched%20sonobuoys%2C%26quot%3B%20Tirk%20and%20Salisbury%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20operators%20must%20manually%20input%20this%20data%20into%20the%20display%20and%20control%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20patents%20are%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpatents-google-com.translate.goog%2Fpatent%2FCN114084285A%2Fzh%3F_x_tr_sl%3Dauto%26_x_tr_tl%3Den%26_x_tr_hl%3Den-US%26_x_tr_hist%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elighter%20sonobuoys%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20improved%20communications%20between%20sonobuoys%20and%20aircraft.%20In%202022%2C%20China%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F03%2F01%2Fchina-us-patents-science-tech%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esurpassed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20America%20in%20number%20of%20patents%20filed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20has%20also%20been%20improving%20the%20quality%20of%20anti-submarine%20training.%20%26quot%3BThe%20PLAN%20has%20acknowledged%20its%20limitations%20and%20has%20begun%20taking%20steps%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20ASW%20training%2C%20both%20in%20simulators%20and%20in%20physical%20training%20environments%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%20%26quot%3BPLAN%20ASW%20units%20are%20training%20under%20more%20realistic%20conditions%2C%20and%20breaking%20down%20administrative%20barriers%20which%20prevented%20them%20from%20generating%20more%20training%20opportunities%20in%20different%20operational%20environments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20since%202015%2C%20training%20materials%20have%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20ASW%20aircraft%20and%20ships%20to%20work%20closely%20together%2C%20which%20is%20standard%20practice%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Western%20navies.%20The%20PLAN%20is%20also%20using%20simulators%20to%20train%20sensor%20and%20weapon%20operators.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20exercise%20involved%20a%20patrol%20aircraft%20transmitting%20target%20data%20to%20a%20command%20ship%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20then%20integrated%20it%20with%20information%20from%20other%20sources%20and%20checked%20the%20information%20against%20a%20target%20information%20database%20to%20confirm%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20target%20was%20an%20enemy%20submarine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CMSI%20report%20noted.%20%26quot%3BThis%20indicated%20both%20a%20potential%20command%20relationship%20from%20command%20vessels%20to%20ASW%20aircraft%20and%20confirmed%20that%20the%20PLAN%20trains%20to%20compare%20potential%20targets%20to%20a%20database%2C%20despite%20its%20small%20(but%20expanding)%20ocean%20surveillance%20and%20intelligence%20collection%20fleet%20and%20a%20nascent%20underwater%20surveillance%20capability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETwitter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-is-developing-systems-to-hunt-us-submarines-from-the-air-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717018261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66575539d0b8e1c832c9cd98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-is-developing-systems-to-hunt-us-submarines-from-the-air-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ch