being%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20made%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20her%20in%20the%20Congo%20easier%20because%20soldiers%20in%20the%20force%20work%20in%20different%20regions%20of%20the%20country%20and%20are%20exposed%20to%20different%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20Sen%20will%20receive%20the%20award%2C%20which%20recognises%20a%20military%20peacekeeper%20who%20has%20best%20integrated%20a%20gender%20perspective%20into%20peacekeeping%20activities%2C%20from%20UN%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20challenge%20of%20ensuring%20that%20peacekeepers%20under%20her%20command%20recognised%20the%20importance%20of%20gender%20and%20socio-cultural%20norms%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Major%20Sen%2C%20who%20served%20with%20the%20Organisation%20Stabilization%20Mission%20in%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20the%20Congo%20(MONUSCO)%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20country%20has%20a%20long%20history.%20It%20has%20its%20own%20culture.%20It%20has%20its%20own%20tradition.%20There%20are%20many%20socio-economic%20issues%20that%20happen.%20But%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20being%20a%20part%20of%20India%2C%20which%20is%20a%20culturally%20rich%20and%20a%20diverse%20country%2C%20and%20especially%20being%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%2C%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20all%20my%20soldiers%20have%20been%20working%20in%20different%20regions%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20they%20have%20served%20in%20different%20terrains%2C%20they%20have%20seen%20different%20environments%2C%20it%20was%20not%20really%20challenging%20for%20me%20to%20have%20a%20team.%20I%20would%20say%20it%20was%20their%20support%20and%20cooperation%20which%20has%20motivated%20me%20and%20helped%20me%20to%20get%20the%20information%20and%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20people%20better.%20So%2C%20(it%20was)%20because%20we%20are%20from%20India%20and%20the%20Indian%20Army%20gives%20you%20all%20the%20opportunity%20and%20exposure%20possible%20(that)%20it%20was%20easy%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20rape%20and%20violence%20being%20used%20as%20an%20implement%20of%20warfare%20in%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20the%20Congo%2C%20Major%20Sen%20said%20it%20is%20very%20important%20for%20peacekeeping%20forces%20to%20have%20a%20gender%20perspective%20because%20it%20helps%20build%20an%20inclusive%20and%20sustainable%20peace%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20any%20conflict%2C%20it%20is%20always%20the%20women%20and%20the%20girls%20who%20are%20more%20affected%20and%20who%20face%20increased%20risk%20of%20abuse.%20So%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20why%20should%20any%20human%20being%20suffer%3F%20As%20women%20peacekeepers%2C%20we%20try%20and%20address%20their%20concerns%20and%20encourage%20them%20to%20raise%20their%20voices%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20explained%20that%20they%20realised%20that%20talking%20to%20the%20country's%20leadership%20wasn't%20enough%20and%20they%20began%20to%20speak%20to%20local%20communities%20to%20get%20a%20better%20idea%20of%20issues%20facing%20the%20people%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20also%20involved%20ourselves%20into%20creating%20awareness%20about%20many%20topics%20that%20concern%20women%2C%20like%20women's%20health%20and%20education%20on%20sexual%20violence%20in%20conflict.%20We%20also%20engaged%20with%20people%20on%20creating%20employment%20training%2C%20like%20baking%20and%20tailoring%20for%20women%20and%20English%20training%20for%20children.%20So%20there%20were%20multiple%20things%20that%20we%20tried%20to%20do%20in%20order%20to%20engage%20with%20people%20which%20could%20help%20us%20address%20their%20concerns%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20also%20spoke%20about%20misinformation%20spread%20against%20MONUSCO%20and%20said%20there%20were%20times%20when%20they%20were%20engaging%20with%20people%20that%20they%20had%20to%20get%20into%20vehicles%20and%20return%20because%20stones%20were%20thrown%20at%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Major%20Switch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20Sen%20graduated%20as%20a%20biotech%20engineer%20and%20was%20pursuing%20a%20Master's%20degree%20from%20IIT%20Bombay%20when%20she%20decided%20to%20join%20the%20Army.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20was%20asked%20about%20what%20made%20her%20make%20the%20switch%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20wanted%20to%20serve%20humanity%20and%20India%2C%20but%20I%20always%20thought%20I%20would%20I'll%20be%20a%20scientist%20and%20do%20it.%20In%20my%20last%20year%20of%20college%2C%20I%20applied%20for%20an%20SSB%20(Service%20Selection%20Board)%2C%20just%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it.%20And%20I%20went%20for%20the%20SSB%20just%20to%20see%20Allahabad%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20will%20see%20a%20new%20place%20and%2C%20somehow%2C%20I%20just%20cleared%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20enjoying%20studying%20-%20I%20love%20science.%20I%20love%20to%20study.%20It%20was%20my%20parents%20who%20have%20taught%20me%20there%20are%20many%20ways%20of%20serving%20mankind%20and%20the%20country%2C%20and%20I%20think%20there's%20no%20better%20way%20for%20me%20to%20do%20it%20than%20what%20I'm%20doing%20now.%20And%20I%20cannot%20be%20happier%20that%20I%20chose%20this%20field%20and%20it's%20just%20really%20good%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717008420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fl7597d1o_major-radhika-sen-un-interview_625x300_30_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-better-way-to-serve-humanity-india-major-set-to-be-honoured-by-un-5774592%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Major%20Radhika%20Sen%2C%20a%20peacekeeper%20who%20served%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20peacekeeping%20mission%20in%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%2C%20was%20pursuing%20