hat%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColleagues%20In%20Dock%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20chief%20minister's%20comments%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20the%20dean%20of%20Sassoon%20Hospital%20-%20%C2%A0where%20two%20doctors%20were%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20replacing%20the%20teenager's%20blood%20samples%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20alcohol%20was%20detected%20in%20them%20-%20claimed%20that%20a%20minister%20and%20an%20MLA%20from%20Mr%20Pawar's%20party%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20asking%20for%20one%20of%20the%20doctors%20to%20be%20made%20the%20head%20of%20the%20forensics%20department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Vinayak%20Kale%20claimed%20that%20the%20letter%20was%20written%20by%20Maharashtra%20Medical%20Education%20Minister%20Hasan%20Mushrif%20and%20MLA%20Sunil%20Tingre%20in%20favour%20of%20Dr%20Ajay%20Tawade%2C%20who%20was%20suspended%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20hospital's%20Forensic%20Medicine%20Department%20on%20Wednesday%20.%20Mr%20Tingre%20is%20already%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20a%20storm%20for%20visiting%20the%20police%20station%20where%20the%20teenager%20was%20taken%20after%20the%20accident%20on%20May%2019%20to%20allegedly%20pressure%20officials%20into%20going%20easy%20on%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kale%20was%20later%20sent%20on%20compulsory%20leave%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20for%20%26quot%3Bfailing%20to%20take%20the%20case%20seriously%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bnot%20taking%20proper%20decisions%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20dean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2018%2C%20the%2017-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20Pune%20realtor%20had%20gone%20partying%20-%20in%20a%20Rs%202.5-crore%20Porsche%20-%20with%20his%20friends%20to%20celebrate%20his%20Class%2012%20results.%20They%20went%20to%20two%20pubs%20and%20drank%20illegally%2C%20paying%20a%20bill%20of%20Rs%2048%2C000%20at%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20then%20got%20into%20the%20Porsche%20with%20two%20of%20his%20friends%20an