0my%20entire%20career%2C%20to%20keep%20my%20life%20balanced%20with%20my%20job.%20In%20my%20book%2C%20I%20write%20about%20my%20Tuesday%20date%20nights%20with%20my%20wife.%20For%20over%20thirty%20years%2C%20I%20had%20a%20hard%20cut-off%20on%20Tuesdays.%20Rain%20or%20shine%2C%20I%20left%20at%20exactly%205%20pm%20and%20spent%20the%20evening%20with%20my%20best%20friend.%20We%20would%20go%20to%20a%20movie%2C%20have%20dinner%2C%20or%20just%20go%20window-shopping%20downtown%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Randolph%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI'm%20Marc%20Randolph%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Netflix%20%26amp%3B%206%20other%20companies.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20is%20my%20definition%20of%20success%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXSbTNRnFfK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FXSbTNRnFfK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Marc%20Randolph%20(%40mbrandolph)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmbrandolph%2Fstatus%2F1795468885245976631%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2066-year-old%20shared%20that%20he%20did%20not%20entertain%20any%20last-minute%20questions%20or%20requests%20on%20Tuesday%20evenings.%20Every%20crisis%20was%20wrapped%20up%20by%205%20pm%20so%20he%20could%20head%20back%20to%20his%20wife.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20had%20something%20to%20say%20to%20me%20on%20Tuesday%20afternoon%20at%204%3A55%2C%20you%20had%20better%20say%20it%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20parking%20lot.%20If%20there%20was%20a%20crisis%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20wrap%20it%20up%20by%205%3A00.%20Those%20Tuesday%20nights%20kept%20me%20sane.%20And%20they%20put%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20work%20in%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcluding%20his%20definition%20of%20success%2C%20Mr%20Randolph%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20resolved%20a%20long%20time%20ago%20to%20not%20be%20one%20of%20those%20entrepreneurs%20on%20their%207th%20startup%20and%20their%207th%20wife.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20thing%20I'm%20most%20proud%20of%20in%20my%20life%20is%20not%20the%20companies%20I%20started%2C%20it's%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20was%20able%20to%20start%20them%20while%20staying%20married%20to%20the%20same%20woman%3B%20having%20my%20kids%20grow%20up%20knowing%20me%20and%20(best%20as%20I%20can%20tell)%20liking%20me%2C%20and%20being%20able%20to%20spend%20time%20pursuing%20the%20other%20passions%20in%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmount-everest-climber-smashes-record-for-fastest-ascent-by-a-woman-5772750%5C%22%3EMount%20Everest%20Climber%20Smashes%20Record%20For%20Fastest%20Ascent%20By%20A%20Woman%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Randolph%20shared%20the%20post%20just%20a%20day%20back.%20Since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20accumulated%20more%20than%20721%2C000%20views%20and%20nearly%2010%2C000%20likes.%20In%20the%20comments%20section%2C%20users%20shared%20their%20thoughts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20this%20definition%20of%20success%20and%20it%20aligns%20closely%20with%20my%20own.%20I've%20said%20sarcastically%20many%20times%20that%20my%20goal%20has%20been%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bsuccessful%20and%20happy%26quot%3B%20and%20these%20components%20of%20a%20personal%20partnership%20and%20family%20and%20time%20for%20them%20and%20myself%20is%20key%20to%20that%20happiness%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20user.%20%26quot%3BNot%20losing%20value%20for%20family%20while%20building%20is%20the%20biggest%20test%20of%20a%20successful%20founder.%20Glad%20you%20aced%20it%2C%20Marc!%26quot%3B%20expressed%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20old%20paradigm%20around%20success%20was%20that%20you%20needed%20to%20achieve%20to%20prove%20your%20worth.%20The%20new%20paradigm%20shift%20around%20success%20is%20that%20you're%20already%20'successful'%20and%20worthy.%20%26quot%3BSuccess%26quot%3B%20is%20simply%20the%20journey%20of%20fulfilment%20and%20growing%20into%20that%20highest%20potential%20you%20were%20born%20with.%20No%20right%20or%20wrong%20in%20how%20you%20choose%20to%20define%20what%20that%20looks%20for%20you.%20Just%20make%20sure%20you've%20adopted%20the%20new%20paradigm%2C%26quot%3B%20commented%20a%20third%20user.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLove%20this.%20True%20definition%20of%20success%20is%20not%20measured%20by%20wealth%20but%20by%20experiences%20and%20time%20spent%20with%20loved%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20shared%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716999480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F6n0uu9vo_marc-randolph_625x300_29_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fim-most-proud-of-netflix-co-founder-shares-his-definition-of-success-5773759%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix%20co-founder%20Marc%20Randolph%20recently%20shared%20his%20definition%20of%20success.%20Taking%20to%20X%2C%20the%2066-year-old%20serial%20entrepreneur%20expressed%20that%20success%20to%20him%20is%20maintaining%20the%20right%20balance%20between%20personal%20and%20professional%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fim-most-proud-of-netflix-co-founder-shares-his-definition-of-success-5773759%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fim-most-proud-of-netflix-co-founder-shares-his-definition-of-success-5773759%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fim-most-proud-of-netflix-co-founder-shares-his-definition-of-success-5773759%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Rubbish-filled%20balloon%20saga%20explained%E2%80%A6%20in%2063%20seconds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716999105000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fne