%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Khul%20gaya%2C%20khul%20gaya%2C%20ab%20aapke%20sheher%20mein%20Pizza%20Galleria%20khul%20gaya%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Pizza%20Galleria%20is%20now%20open%20in%20your%20town%2Fcity)%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20practice%20is%20followed%20by%20him%20even%20today.%20Every%20time%20a%20new%20store%20opens%2C%20he%20rides%20around%20the%20city%20shouting%20these%20slogans%2C%20followed%20by%20distributing%20pamphlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED-day%20arrived%20on%2025%20December%202015%2C%20when%20many%20people%20in%20Gohana%20tasted%20their%20first%20fresh-dough%20pizza.%20To%20entice%20customers%2C%20he%20offered%20the%20first%20300%20pizzas%20free%2C%20a%20practice%20followed%20even%20today%20at%20all%20new%20outlets.%20Slowly%20and%20steadily%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20ambience%20and%20novelty%20of%20pizzas%2C%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base%20was%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20with%20a%20limited%20menu%20of%20seven%20to%20eight%20pizzas%2C%20garlic%20bread%2C%20and%20some%20pasta.%20It%20took%20almost%20a%20year%20for%20Sandeep%E2%80%99s%20pizza%20venture%20to%20taste%20success%20in%20Gohana.%20The%20biggest%20challenge%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20was%20teaching%20people%20to%20try%20a%20new%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20so%20special%20about%20a%20fresh%20dough%20pizza%20or%20even%20how%20to%20eat%20it.%20Just%20like%20me%2C%20they%20too%20thought%20of%20it%20like%20a%20fat%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20a%20different%20%3Cem%3Echutney%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sauce).%20I%20also%20had%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20food%20was%20perfect%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20experienced%20chefs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20overcame%20this%20challenge%20by%20building%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedures%20(SOPs)%20to%20be%20followed%20for%20making%20the%20pizzas%2C%20and%20then%20serving%2C%20packing%2C%20and%20delivering%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20employment%20in%20small%20towns%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20as%20the%20people%20of%20Gohana%20accepted%20and%20thronged%20to%20Pizza%20Galleria%2C%20Sandeep%20knew%20he%20was%20on%20the%20right%20track.%20This%20led%20him%20to%20open%20the%20next%20store%20in%20Panipat%20and%20Ganaur%20(Haryana)%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sandeep%20with%20his%20team%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220-300x150.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220-500x250.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220-768x384.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220-150x75.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351209%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESandeep%20has%20provided%20employment%20to%20over%20700%20people%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20looking%20back.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%2072%20stores%2C%20which%20include%20company-owned%20outlets%20as%20well%20as%20franchise%20outlets%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20and%20Chandigarh.%20With%20this%2C%20he%20also%20has%20been%20able%20to%20provide%20employment%20to%20over%20700%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20feel%20proud%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20create%20such%20a%20large%20family%20through%20Pizza%20Galleria.%20We%20had%20a%20meetup%20where%20we%20had%20invited%20over%20100%20staff%20members%20to%20Karnal.%20Seeing%20so%20many%20people%20together%20who%20are%20doing%20well%20today%20is%20my%20biggest%20accomplishment%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sandeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%20was%20also%20joined%20by%20his%20friend%20Ishan%20Chugh%20as%20a%20co-founder%20in%202017%20after%20the%20third%20outlet%20was%20opened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPizza%20Galleria%20serves%20pizza%2C%20pasta%2C%20garlic%20bread%2C%20sandwiches%2C%20fries%2C%20burgers%2C%20soft%20drinks%20and%20more.%20Their%20pizzas%20start%20at%20Rs%2069%20and%20their%20combos%20start%20at%20Rs%2089.%20Their%20bestsellers%20are%20the%20%3Cem%3Etandoori%20paneer%3C%2Fem%3E%20pizza%2C%20pizza%20galleria%20exotica%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Emakhni%3C%2Fem%3E%20pizza%2C%20and%20also%20offers%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBaahubali%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%2024-inch%20pizza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20USP%2C%20apart%20from%20being%20vegetarian%2C%20is%20their%20tomato%20sauce%20and%20cheesy%20liquid%20sauce%2C%20which%20adds%20to%20the%20flavour%20of%20the%20pizza%2C%20states%20Sandeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%20and%20Ishan%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20season%203.%20While%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20able%20to%20land%20a%20deal%2C%20it%20created%20a%20massive%20increase%20in%20demand%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founder.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20received%20over%204%2C000%20enquiry%20calls%20from%20people%20interested%20in%20opening%20franchise%20outlets.%20It%20will%20help%20us%20achieve%20our%20vision%20of%20opening%20500%20outlets%20by%202030%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sandeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandeep%E2%80%99s%20dream%20is%20to%20create%20an%20Indian%20brand%20with%20footprints%20across%20the%20world.%20His%20biggest%20validation%2C%20he%20says%2C%20eventually%20came%20from%20his%20father%20who%20praised%20Sandeep%20for%20his%20exceptional%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20dreams%20came%20true%20through%20Pizza%20Galleria.%20From%20drawing%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%209%2C000%20per%20month%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20buy%20my%20own%20house%20and%20car.%20What%20matters%20most%20to%20me%20is%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20praise%2C%20which%20is%20something%20money%20can%E2%80%99t%20buy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sandeep%20had%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303449%2Fmumbai-duo-quit-job-to-make-authentic-neapolitan-pizza-earn-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20bite%20of%20pizza%20in%202014%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20little%20did%20he%20know%20that%20he%20would%20be%20selling%20over%207%20lakh%20pizzas%20a%20month%20a%20decade%20later!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWork%20hard%20to%20fulfil%20your%20dreams.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20yourself%20from%20achieving%20big%20dreams%20because%20you%E2%80%99re%20from%20a%20small%20town.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20best%20time%20to%20start%20a%20business.%20Start%20small%3B%20even%20food%20carts%20have%20turned%20into%20massive%20businesses.%20Live%20your%20life%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20it%20becomes%20an%20example%20for%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Sandeep%20Jangra%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716817228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsandeep-1716813220.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351202%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20his%20first%20bite%20of%20pizza%2C%20Sandeep%20Jangra%20opened%20the%20first%20Pizza%20Galleria%20outlet%20in%20Gohana%2C%20Haryana.%20Today%2C%20his%20vegetarian%20pizza%20chain%20has%2072%20outlets%20across%20India%2C%20selling%20over%2020%2C000%20pizzas%20daily%2C%20and%20employing%20over%20700%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22