02.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmini-tray-gardens-1-1716437248-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350855%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESharda%20owns%20at%20least%2070%20visually%20appealing%20and%20intricately%20designed%20miniature%20gardens%20on%20various%20themes.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDraw%20a%20rough%20sketch%20of%20the%20theme%20of%20your%20garden%20in%20mind%20and%20select%20a%20suitable%20tray%20based%20on%20its%20size%2C%20shape%2C%20and%20material%20like%20mud%20and%20ceramic.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFill%20the%20tray%20with%20potting%20mix%20to%20create%20a%20base%20for%20your%20garden.%20Mix%2050%20percent%20of%20fertile%20soil%20with%2015%20percent%20cow%20dung%2C%2015%20percent%20cocopeat%2C%20and%2010%20percent%20perlite%20and%20bone%20meal%20each.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPlant%20small%20and%20dwarf%20varieties%20of%20plants%20like%20succulents%2C%20snake%20plants%2C%20syngonium%2C%20jade%20and%20spider%20plants.%20Water%20it%20and%20press%20the%20soil%20from%20above%20to%20let%20it%20settle.%20It%20takes%20roughly%20an%20hour%20to%20settle%20the%20soil%20in%20summer.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELater%20on%2C%20build%20your%20pathways%2C%20huts%2C%20or%20other%20structures.%20Decorate%20your%20garden%20with%20colourful%20pebbles%2C%20hedges%2C%20bells%2C%20dolls%2C%20and%20other%20decorative%20items.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWater%20the%20tray%20using%20a%20spray%20bottle%2C%20carefully.%20You%20can%20also%20spray%20liquid%20compost%20using%20kitchen%20waste%20like%20banana%2C%20garlic%2C%20ginger%2C%20and%20onion%20peels%20to%20fertilise%20soil%20and%20prevent%20the%20plant%20from%20fungal%20attacks.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ETo%20make%20the%20compost%2C%20collect%20peels%20in%20a%20bucket%20and%20add%20some%20water%20to%20it.%20After%20two%20to%20three%20days%2C%20strain%20the%20contents%20and%20mix%20it%20with%20clean%20water%20in%20a%20ratio%20of%201%3A2.%20Spray%20this%20fertiliser%20on%20all%20tray%20gardens%20every%20two%20to%20three%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharda%20says%20it%20takes%20her%20roughly%2020%20minutes%20to%20decorate%20the%20tray%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20get%20bored%2C%20I%20recreate%20these%20tray%20gardens%20using%20the%20same%20plants%20and%20props.%20Just%20like%20kids%20play%20with%20their%20miniature%20dollhouses%2C%20I%20have%20my%20tray%20gardens.%20My%20friends%20say%20I%20have%20gone%20back%20to%20my%20childhood%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Sharda%20Godara.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716813891000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmini-tray-gardens-2-1716437290.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350852%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharda%20Godara%20transformed%20her%20Faridabad%20home%20into%20a%20mini%20jungle%20with%201%2C000%20plants.%20She%20now%20enjoys%20crafting%20miniature%20tray%20gardens%20around%20various%20themes%2C%20and%20shares%20five%20steps%20to%20create%20them%20at%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350852%2Fhow-to-make-miniature-tray-gardens-at-home-steps-faridabad-sharda-godara-urban-gardener%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20The%20%E2%80%98Eco%20Village%20Lady%E2%80%99%20of%20India%20Who%20Uses%20Solar%20Energy%20to%20Power%20Villages%20in%20Ladakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETo%20create%20a%20revolution%2C%20one%20has%20to%20step%20outside%20one%E2%80%99s%20comfort%20zone.%20This%20became%20clear%20to%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Neha%20Upadhyaya%20right%20at%20the%20outset%20of%20her%20quest%20to%20transform%20the%20rural%20hinterland%20of%20India%2C%20with%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20Ladakhi%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20now%20a%20decade%20since%20that%20bold%20decision%2C%20and%20Upadhyaya%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20prouder%20of%20the%20ripple%20effect%20her%20efforts%20created%20%E2%80%94%20impacting%20more%20than%203%2C000%20women%20through%20her%20platform%20Guna%20Organics%20and%20also%20playing%20a%20role%20in%20eight%20rural%20nooks%20being%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335875%2Fgoa-stay-lawyer-panta-ferrao-built-khaama-kethna-eco-village-jungle-retreat-tree-house-cottage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebranded%20as%20ecovillages%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Her%20venture%20Guna%20Organics%20under%20Vishwadeep%20Trust%20integrates%20organic%20practices%20and%20solar%20technology%20in%20farming.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpadhyaya%E2%80%99s%20journey%20has%20been%20fraught%20with%20obstacles%20and%20wins%2C%20the%20former%20often%20being%20precursors%20to%20the%20latter%2C%20she%20points%20out.%20Take%20for%20instance%20the%20time%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20relieve%20herself%20near%20an%20animal%20shed%20in%20Tukla%20village.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20sanitation%20woes%20became%20evident%20to%20her%20and%20she%20began%20advocating%20for%20public%20toilets.%20Today%2C%20the%20set%20of%20public%20toilets%20for%20women%20that%20stand%20in%20the%20Tukla%20and%20Urbis%20villages%20is%20the%20result%20of%20months%20of%20effort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20villagers%20of%20Ladakh%20know%20her%20as%20the%20woman%20who%20has%20fought%20the%20authorities%20on%20their%20behalf%2C%20Upadhyaya%20says%20she%20is%20simply%20a%20changemaker.%20She%20calls%20herself%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336971%2Fcourse-in-social-impact-for-changemakers-sp-jain-institute-post-graduate-programme-in-development-management%2F%5C%22%20t