figcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20of%20Vishwadeep%20Trust%20conducts%20drives%20to%20educate%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20against%20plastic%20and%20litter%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vishwadeep%20Trust%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20the%20way%2C%20there%20have%20been%20multiple%20boosts%20to%20her%20efforts%2C%20sometimes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20and%20other%20times%20in%20the%20form%20of%20mentorship%20opportunities.%20The%20most%20significant%2C%20she%20recalls%2C%20is%20being%20a%20part%20of%20the%20cohort%20of%20the%20Women%20Entrepreneurship%20Platform%20(WEP)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20first-of-its-kind%2C%20unified%20access%20portal%20incubated%20by%20NITI%20Aayog.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20brings%20together%20women%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20India%20to%20build%20a%20nurturing%20ecosystem%20that%20enables%20them%20to%20realise%20their%20entrepreneurial%20aspirations%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20mentorship%2C%20access%20to%20funding%20opportunities%2C%20personalised%20guidance%20and%20networking%20opportunities%20with%20industry%20experts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20wealth%20of%20experience%20she%20gained%20from%20WEP%E2%80%99s%20Unnati%20program%2C%20a%20collaboration%3Cbr%3Ewith%20Microsave%20Consulting%20and%20the%20Small%20Industries%20Development%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SIDBI)%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20supporting%20women-led%20enterprises%20in%20the%20green%20sector%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%2015%20women%20in%20green%20ventures%20who%20were%20a%20part%20of%20this.%20We%20are%20all%20trying%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20change.%20It%20is%20great%20to%20be%20around%20people%20who%20have%20the%20same%20struggle%20as%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%20that%20there%20are%20a%20host%20of%20useful%20online%20courses%20and%20customised%20sessions%20made%20available%20for%20women%20through%20WEP%20and%20its%20program%20partners.%20She%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20put%20us%20in%20paired%20each%20one%20of%20us%20with%20mentors%20who%20help%20us%20foster%20connections%20with%20relevant%20industry%20experts.%20The%20aim%20is%20to%20make%20us%20fully%20ready.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20associations%20like%20these%20that%20champion%20the%20revolution%20Upadhyaya%20is%20attempting%20to%20create.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20lies%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20eco-villages%20she%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20creating.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20microcosm%20of%20change%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefined%20as%20%E2%80%9Can%20intentional%2C%20traditional%20or%20urban%20community%20that%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333558%2Fbest-farm-stays-in-india-with-natural-pool-organic-food-slow-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsciously%20designed%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20locally-owned%20participatory%20processes%20in%20all%20four%20dimensions%20of%20sustainability%20(social%2C%20culture%2C%20ecology%20and%20economy)%20to%20regenerate%20social%20and%20natural%20environments%E2%80%9D%2C%20an%20eco-village%20is%20a%20challenging%20concept.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Upadhyaya%20set%20out%20to%20give%20Takmachik%20village%20in%20Ladakh%20a%20sustainable%20makeover%2C%20she%20understood%20that%20social%2C%20cultural%2C%20and%20ecological%20systems%20weren%E2%80%99t%20the%20only%20factors%20to%20navigate.%20The%20villagers%E2%80%99%20mindsets%20needed%20a%20change%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20along%20with%20instilling%20sustainable%20measures%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20renewable%20energy%20resources%2C%20recycling%2C%20plastic%20alternatives%20and%20sanitation%20drives%20%E2%80%94%20she%20began%20convincing%20the%20villagers%20to%20broaden%20their%20horizons%20when%20it%20came%20to%20farming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20were%20dependent%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255790%2Fslug-ladakh-save-crores-village-dah-hanu-valley-apricots-trees-yellow-tail-moth-pest-tsering-stobdan-pest-eradication-organic-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20apricot%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20rightly%20so%2C%20a%20major%20portion%20of%20the%20revenue%20is%20generated%20through%20its%20sale%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20But%20a%20little%20probing%20led%20her%20to%20discover%20that%20a%20kilo%20of%20apricots%20was%20retailing%20for%20just%20Rs%20150.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-6-1716443110.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20back%20belts%20that%20Upadhyaya%20has%20given%20the%20women%20help%20ease%20their%20struggle%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-6-1716443110.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-6-1716443110-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-6-1716443110-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-6-1716443110-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-6-1716443110-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350874%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20back%20belts%20that%20Upadhyaya%20has%20given%20the%20women%20help%20ease%20their%20struggle%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vishwadeep%20Trust%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22