0machines%20that%20save%20time%2C%20or%20hire%20labourers%20to%20do%20the%20work%20causing%20a%20significant%20dent%20in%20their%20already%20low%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20teenager%20looked%20for%20solutions%2C%20he%20remembered%20seeing%20his%20grandfather%20using%20a%20manual%20machine%20to%20remove%20weeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECould%20he%20modify%20it%20by%20making%20it%20electric%20and%20add%20multiple%20options%20using%20technology%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20farmers%20around%20me%2C%20including%20my%20father%2C%20used%20to%20rent%20tractors%20and%20other%20machines%20to%20sow%20seeds%20and%20remove%20weeds.%20The%20other%20option%20was%20to%20hire%20labourers%20for%2010-12%20days.%20Both%20options%20caused%20a%20lot%20of%20expense%20to%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Ramdhan%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2015%2C%20he%20sketched%20the%20first%20prototype%20of%20this%20machine%20and%20submitted%20the%20entry%20at%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20INSPIRE%20Award%20%E2%80%93%20MANAK%20(Million%20Minds%20Augmenting%20National%20Aspiration%20and%20Knowledge).%20He%20won%20the%20award%20and%20received%20a%20prize%20money%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%2C%20which%20he%20used%20to%20build%20his%20first%20prototype.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20machine%20that%20would%20do%20multiple%20tasks.%20I%20wanted%20to%20prevent%20farmers%20from%20lugging%20around%2010%20litre%20spray%20pumps%20on%20their%20shoulders%2C%20which%20you%20have%20to%20refill%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20his%20sketch%2C%20some%20old%20cycles%20and%20went%20to%20a%20welder%20who%20helped%20him%20make%20the%20machine.%20His%20first%20prototype%20was%20a%20machine%20which%20could%20sow%20seeds%20and%20spray%20pesticides.%20Ramdhan%20laughs%20as%20he%20shares%20that%20his%20machine%20is%20a%20product%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejugaad%3C%